OL,3,CDonaldson set for court appearance for
OL,4,Copening of sex offences trial
OL,6,FFormer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,7,FDonaldson is set to return to Newry
OL,8,FCrown Court today for the first time
OL,9,Fin more than a year as a jury is sworn
OL,10,Fin for the start of his trial.
OL,12,FThe 63-year-old has been charged with
OL,13,Fand denies 18 alleged child sex
OL,14,Foffences allegedly involving two
OL,15,Fvictims.
OL,17,FThey include claims of rape, gross
OL,18,Findecency and indecent assault. It is
OL,19,Falleged the offences were committed
OL,20,Fover a 20-year period between 1985 and
OL,21,F2008.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
