PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779822664
OL,3,CDonaldson set for court appearance for
OL,4,Copening of sex offences trial
OL,6,FLady Eleanor Donaldson will not be in
OL,7,Fcourt.
OL,9,FTo avoid any confusion. Sir Jeffrey
OL,10,FDonaldson is facing a normal criminal
OL,11,Ftrial.
OL,13,FIt is just over two years since the
OL,14,Fcouple first appeared in Newry Crown
OL,15,FCourt charged with historic child sex
OL,16,Foffences which they have always denied.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
