PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1779822664
OL,3,CDonaldson set for court appearance for
OL,4,Copening of sex offences trial
OL,6,FThe previous month - when the news
OL,7,Fbroke of their arrest, search at their
OL,8,FCo Down home, and subsequent charges -
OL,9,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson's long-standing
OL,10,Fpolitical career came to a shuddering
OL,11,Fhalt.
OL,13,FThat included his resignation as
OL,14,Fleader of the DUP.
OL,16,FThis trial is expected to last four
OL,17,Fweeks or more and given the peer's
OL,18,Fhigh-profile - is expected to attract
OL,19,Fsignificant attention.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
